            <![CDATA[
            <p>I figured out why Fastmail forwarding appeared not to be working. I was sending the test email from the same account the forward was going to. Evidently, when you do that, it doesn't trigger a forward. I'm not getting a lot of email through Fastmail now, but I did get one this morning, and the forwarding worked as expected. </p>
